What is the output of the following code?
```java
public static int[] doubleAll(int[] arr) {
    int[] result = new int[arr.length];
    for (int i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) {
        result[i] = arr[i] * 2;
    }
    return result;
}
// In main:
int[] nums = {1, 2, 3};
int[] doubled = doubleAll(nums);
System.out.println(nums[0] + " " + doubled[0]);
```

